| 2 | **Inconsistent Error Handling** | `server.py` returns structured JSON errors via `_error_response()`. `gemini_service.py` mixes return-error-dicts with raising `RuntimeError`. `code_executor.py` returns error dicts. `data_service.py` raises exceptions. No unified pattern. | All backend files |
